Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Translator: Gulnoza Yakubova
Reviewer: Adham Kurbanov

00:00:15.260 --> 00:00:17.260
Men savantman (ko'p narsa biluvchi, autismning bir turi)

00:00:17.260 --> 00:00:19.260
yoki aniqrog'i,

00:00:19.260 --> 00:00:21.260
yuqori faoliyatli

00:00:21.260 --> 00:00:23.260
autistik savantman.

00:00:23.260 --> 00:00:25.260
Bu noyob holat.

00:00:25.260 --> 00:00:28.260
Mening holatimdagiek

00:00:28.260 --> 00:00:30.260
o'zlikni anglash va

00:00:30.260 --> 00:00:32.260
tilni mukammal egallash qobiliyati

00:00:32.260 --> 00:00:35.260
bilan birga kelganda yanada noyobroq holatdir.

00:00:35.260 --> 00:00:38.260
Ko'pincha, men biror kimsa bilan uchrashganimda,

00:00:38.260 --> 00:00:40.260
ular mening bu holatimni bilishadi va

00:00:40.260 --> 00:00:43.260
ularda ma'lum bir turdagi noqulaylik bo'ladi.

00:00:43.260 --> 00:00:46.260
Men buni ularning ko'zlarida ko'ra olaman.

00:00:46.260 --> 00:00:49.260
Ular mendan nimanidir so'rashni xohlaydilar.

00:00:49.260 --> 00:00:51.260
Va nihoyat, juda ko'p holatda,

00:00:51.260 --> 00:00:54.260
ishtiyoq odatdagidan kuchliroq

00:00:54.260 --> 00:00:56.260
va ular darrov o'ylamasdan gapirib yuboradilar:

00:00:56.260 --> 00:00:58.260
"Agar men sizga tug'ilgan sanamni aytsam,

00:00:58.260 --> 00:01:00.260
haftaning qaysi kunida tug'ilganligimni aytib bera olasizmi?"

00:01:00.260 --> 00:01:03.260
(Kulgi)

00:01:03.260 --> 00:01:06.260
Yoki kub ildizlarni

00:01:06.260 --> 00:01:10.260
yoki uzun raqam yoki matnni yoddan aytib berishimni so'raydilar.

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:12.260
Agar men bugun sizlarga

00:01:12.260 --> 00:01:15.260
bir savant kishining ko'rsatuvini

00:01:15.260 --> 00:01:19.260
ijro etmasam meni kechirasizlar deb umid qilaman.

00:01:19.260 --> 00:01:22.260
Uning o'rniga men

00:01:22.260 --> 00:01:24.260
tug'ilgan sanalar yoki

00:01:24.260 --> 00:01:26.260
kub ildizlaridan ancha qiziqarliroq,

00:01:26.260 --> 00:01:29.260
mening ishimdan ko'ra

00:01:29.260 --> 00:01:31.260
ongimga biroz

00:01:31.260 --> 00:01:34.260
chuqurroq va ancha yaqinroq narsa haqida gapiraman.

00:01:34.260 --> 00:01:36.260
Men sizlarga ong, tushuncha haqida

00:01:36.260 --> 00:01:39.260
qisqagina gapirib bermoqchiman.

00:01:39.260 --> 00:01:42.260
U o'zining ismini mashhur qiladigan pyesa va

00:01:42.260 --> 00:01:44.260
qisqa hikoyalar yozayotganida,

00:01:44.260 --> 00:01:47.260
Anton Chekhov o'z atrofidagi

00:01:47.260 --> 00:01:49.260
dunyoni kuzatganlarini

00:01:49.260 --> 00:01:51.260
yozib boradigan

00:01:51.260 --> 00:01:53.260
kundalik daftari bo'lgan edi --

00:01:53.260 --> 00:01:55.260
boshqa kishilar e'tibor bermay qoladigan

00:01:55.260 --> 00:01:58.260
kichkina parchalarni, qismlarni yozib borar edi.

00:01:58.260 --> 00:02:01.260
Har safar Chekhovni va uning

00:02:01.260 --> 00:02:05.260
inson hayotining o'ziga xos tasavvurini o'qiganimda,

00:02:05.260 --> 00:02:07.260
bu menga mening ham nima sababdan yozuvchi

00:02:07.260 --> 00:02:09.260
bo'lganligimni eslatadi.

00:02:09.260 --> 00:02:11.260
Men kitoblarimda

00:02:11.260 --> 00:02:13.260
ong tabiatini o'rganaman

00:02:13.260 --> 00:02:16.260
ongning har xil turlari qanday qilib

00:02:16.260 --> 00:02:18.260
bilish va tushunishning har xil turlarini paydo

00:02:18.260 --> 00:02:21.260
qilishini o'rganaman.

00:02:23.260 --> 00:02:25.260
Mening ishimdan kelib chiqqan

00:02:25.260 --> 00:02:27.260
mana bu uchta savol.

00:02:27.260 --> 00:02:29.260
Bularga javobni o'ylab o'tirgandan ko'ra,

00:02:29.260 --> 00:02:32.260
Sizlarga iltimosim bor,

00:02:32.260 --> 00:02:34.260
siz bu savollarga qarashingiz bilan

00:02:34.260 --> 00:02:36.260
boshingiz va yuragingizda

00:02:36.260 --> 00:02:38.260
sodir bo'layotgan sezgi va chuqur ichki sezgiga

00:02:38.260 --> 00:02:41.260
bir soniya mobaynida e'tibor bering

00:02:41.260 --> 00:02:44.260
Masalan, hisoblash.

00:02:44.260 --> 00:02:46.260
Yechimi raqamlar chizig'ining qayerida

00:02:46.260 --> 00:02:49.260
joylashishini seza olasizmi?

00:02:49.260 --> 00:02:52.260
Yoki chet tilidagi so'zga va tovushlarga e'tibor bering.

00:02:52.260 --> 00:02:54.260
Bu zo'zlarning nimaligini anglash uchun

00:02:54.260 --> 00:02:57.260
bir necha ma'nolarni ayta olasizmi?

00:02:57.260 --> 00:03:00.260
Shoirlik sohasida esa,

00:03:00.260 --> 00:03:02.260
nima uchun shoir 'uy quyoni' o'rninga

00:03:02.260 --> 00:03:05.260
'yovvoyi quyon' so'zini ishlatadi.

00:03:06.260 --> 00:03:08.260
Men sizlarning shu narsani bajarishingizni xohlayman,

00:03:08.260 --> 00:03:12.260
chunki ishonamanki, bizning shaxsiy tushunchamiz

00:03:12.260 --> 00:03:14.260
ilmni qanday egallashimizning

00:03:14.260 --> 00:03:16.260
eng asosidir.

00:03:16.260 --> 00:03:18.260
Mavhum fikr mulohazalardan ko'ra

00:03:18.260 --> 00:03:21.260
estetik fikr mulohazalar

00:03:21.260 --> 00:03:23.260
biz hammamiz biladigan narsani

00:03:23.260 --> 00:03:26.260
bilishimizdagi jarayonni

00:03:26.260 --> 00:03:28.260
boshqarib, shakllantiradi.

00:03:28.260 --> 00:03:31.260
Men buning juda yaqqol misoliman.

00:03:31.260 --> 00:03:34.260
Mendagi so'z va raqamlar dunyosi

00:03:34.260 --> 00:03:36.260
rang, his-tuyg'u va

00:03:36.260 --> 00:03:38.260
shahsiyat bilan aralashadi.

00:03:38.260 --> 00:03:40.260
Huanning (Juan) aytishicha,

00:03:40.260 --> 00:03:43.260
bu olimlar sinesteziya deb ataydigan holat,

00:03:43.260 --> 00:03:45.260
ya'ni, his-tuyg'ular orasida

00:03:45.260 --> 00:03:48.260
o'zaro g'ayrioddiy suhbatdir.

00:03:51.260 --> 00:03:53.260
Mana birdan 12 gacha bo'lgan raqamlar,

00:03:53.260 --> 00:03:55.260
mening ko'rishimcha --

00:03:55.260 --> 00:03:59.260
har bir raqamning o'ziga hos shakli va hususiyatlari bor.

00:03:59.260 --> 00:04:01.260
Bir - oppoq yorug'likning cho'g'i.

00:04:01.260 --> 00:04:06.260
Olti - juda kichkina va juda g'amgin qora teshik.

00:04:06.260 --> 00:04:09.260
Bu chizmalar bu yerda qora va oq rangda,

00:04:09.260 --> 00:04:11.260
lekin mening ongimda ularning rangi bor.

00:04:11.260 --> 00:04:13.260
Uch - yashil.

00:04:13.260 --> 00:04:15.260
To'rt - ko'k.

00:04:15.260 --> 00:04:18.260
Besh - sariq.

00:04:20.260 --> 00:04:22.260
Men rasm ham chizaman.

00:04:22.260 --> 00:04:25.260
Mana bu rasmlarimdan bittasi.

00:04:25.260 --> 00:04:29.260
Bu ikkita tub sonning ko'paytmasi.

00:04:29.260 --> 00:04:31.260
Uch o'lchamli shakllar

00:04:31.260 --> 00:04:34.260
va o'rtada ular hosil qiladigan bo'shliq

00:04:34.260 --> 00:04:36.260
yangi shaklni hosil qiladi,

00:04:36.260 --> 00:04:39.260
bu esa ko'paytmaning javobi.

00:04:39.260 --> 00:04:41.260
Kattaroq raqamlarchi?

00:04:41.260 --> 00:04:45.260
Matematik konstanta - Pi dan ancha kattaroq sonni

00:04:45.260 --> 00:04:47.260
bunday tasavvur qila olmaysiz.

00:04:47.260 --> 00:04:49.260
Bu cheksiz son --

00:04:49.260 --> 00:04:51.260
cheksiz davom etaveradi,

00:04:51.260 --> 00:04:53.260
Pi ning birinchi 20ta o'nlik kasrini

00:04:53.260 --> 00:04:57.260
chizgan mana bu rasmimda

00:04:57.260 --> 00:04:59.260
ranglar,

00:04:59.260 --> 00:05:02.260
hissiyotlar va yuzasi, ya'ni tuzilishini olib,

00:05:02.260 --> 00:05:04.260
ularning hammasini

00:05:04.260 --> 00:05:09.260
past-tepalik raqamli landshaft kabi birga tasvirladim.

00:05:09.260 --> 00:05:12.260
Lekin, men rangli ko'radiganim, faqatgina raqamlar emas.

00:05:12.260 --> 00:05:14.260
Men uchun so'zlar ham

00:05:14.260 --> 00:05:16.260
ranglar va hissiyotlar

00:05:16.260 --> 00:05:18.260
va tuzilishga ega.

00:05:18.260 --> 00:05:20.260
Mana bu "Lolita" romanidan

00:05:20.260 --> 00:05:22.260
eng avvalgi ibora.

00:05:22.260 --> 00:05:26.260
Nabokovning o'zi ham synestetik edi.

00:05:26.260 --> 00:05:28.260
Ko'rib turibsizki,

00:05:28.260 --> 00:05:31.260
mening L tovushini tushunishim

00:05:31.260 --> 00:05:33.260
alliteratsiyani ajratishimga

00:05:33.260 --> 00:05:36.260
darrov yordam beradi.

00:05:36.260 --> 00:05:38.260
Boshqa bir misol:

00:05:38.260 --> 00:05:40.260
bu biroz matematikaga hos.

00:05:40.260 --> 00:05:42.260
Orangizda kimdir "The Great Gatsby" ("Buyuk Getsbi") dan

00:05:42.260 --> 00:05:44.260
olingan gapning tuzilishini

00:05:44.260 --> 00:05:47.260
sezarmikansiz.

00:05:48.260 --> 00:05:51.260
Bu yerda bo'g'inlarning bir biriga moslashib kelishi bor --

00:05:51.260 --> 00:05:53.260
wheat - bir bo'g'in;

00:05:53.260 --> 00:05:55.260
prairies, ikki bo'g'in;

00:05:55.260 --> 00:05:58.260
lost Swede towna, uch bo'gin --

00:05:58.260 --> 00:06:00.260
bir, ikki, uch.

00:06:00.260 --> 00:06:04.260
Bu ongga yoqimli ta'sir ko'rsatadi

00:06:04.260 --> 00:06:06.260
va gapning to'g'ri

00:06:06.260 --> 00:06:09.260
bo'lib tuyulishiga yordam beradi.

00:06:09.260 --> 00:06:11.260
Bir oz avval men sizlarga

00:06:11.260 --> 00:06:14.260
bergan savollarga qaytaylik.

00:06:14.260 --> 00:06:17.260
64 ni 75 ga ko'paytirish.

00:06:17.260 --> 00:06:20.260
Agar ba'zilarining shaxmat o'ynasangiz,

00:06:20.260 --> 00:06:22.260
64 kvadrat raqam

00:06:22.260 --> 00:06:25.260
ekanligini bilasiz,

00:06:25.260 --> 00:06:27.260
va shaxmat doskasida

00:06:27.260 --> 00:06:29.260
sakkizga sakkiz,

00:06:29.260 --> 00:06:32.260
ya'ni 64 kataklar bor.

00:06:32.260 --> 00:06:34.260
Hullas, bu bizga biz tasavvur qila oladigan,

00:06:34.260 --> 00:06:37.260
his qila oladigan shaklni beradi.

00:06:37.260 --> 00:06:40.260
75 chi?

00:06:40.260 --> 00:06:42.260
Ho'sh, agar 100,

00:06:42.260 --> 00:06:45.260
agar biz yuzni kvadratdek tasavvur qilsak,

00:06:45.260 --> 00:06:48.260
75 mana bunga o'xshaydi.

00:06:48.260 --> 00:06:50.260
Endi qiladigan ishimiz esa

00:06:50.260 --> 00:06:52.260
ana o'sha ikkita rasmni

00:06:52.260 --> 00:06:54.260
ongimizda mana bunday

00:06:54.260 --> 00:06:57.260
birga qo'yishdir.

00:06:57.260 --> 00:07:01.260
64 -- 6400 bo'ladi.

00:07:01.260 --> 00:07:05.260
O'ng burchakda

00:07:05.260 --> 00:07:07.260
hech narsani hisoblashning keragi yo'q.

00:07:07.260 --> 00:07:09.260
bu tomonlama to'rt, tepaga va pastga to'rt --

00:07:09.260 --> 00:07:12.260
16 bo'ladi.

00:07:12.260 --> 00:07:14.260
Natijasini topish ucun

00:07:14.260 --> 00:07:16.260
16, 16 va 16 ni

00:07:16.260 --> 00:07:19.260
olish kerak.

00:07:19.260 --> 00:07:21.260
Bu esa maktabda sizga matematik hisoblashni

00:07:21.260 --> 00:07:24.260
o'rgatgandan ancha osonroq. Bunga ishonchim komil.

00:07:24.260 --> 00:07:26.260
Bu 16 + 16 + 16 = 48,

00:07:26.260 --> 00:07:28.260
4800 --

00:07:28.260 --> 00:07:30.260
4000

00:07:30.260 --> 00:07:33.260
misolni javobi.

00:07:33.260 --> 00:07:35.260
Qanday bajarishni bilsangiz oson.

00:07:35.260 --> 00:07:38.260
(Kulgi)

00:07:38.260 --> 00:07:41.260
Ikkinchi savol Islandcha so'z edi.

00:07:41.260 --> 00:07:44.260
Bu yerda Islandcha gapiradigan odamlar

00:07:44.260 --> 00:07:46.260
ko'p emas deb o'ylayman.

00:07:46.260 --> 00:07:49.260
Shunday ekan, javob turini ikkitaga keltiray.

00:07:51.260 --> 00:07:53.260
Hnuggin:

00:07:53.260 --> 00:07:55.260
Bu quvnoq so'zmi,

00:07:55.260 --> 00:07:57.260
yoki g'amgin so'zmi?

00:07:57.260 --> 00:07:59.260
Nima deysiz?

00:08:00.260 --> 00:08:02.260
Ho'p.

00:08:02.260 --> 00:08:04.260
Ba'zi odamlar buni quvnoq so'z deydilar.

00:08:04.260 --> 00:08:06.260
Ko'p odamlar, ko'pchiligi,

00:08:06.260 --> 00:08:08.260
buni g'amgin so'z deydilar.

00:08:08.260 --> 00:08:12.260
Aslida, bu g'amgin degan ma'noni anglatadi.

00:08:12.260 --> 00:08:15.260
(Kulgi)

00:08:15.260 --> 00:08:18.260
Statistik jihatdan, nimaga

00:08:18.260 --> 00:08:20.260
ko'pchilik odamlar

00:08:20.260 --> 00:08:22.260
so'zni bu holatda g'amgin deb aytadilar,

00:08:22.260 --> 00:08:25.260
boshqa holatlarda esa og'ir deydilar?

00:08:25.260 --> 00:08:28.260
Mening nazariyotim bo'yicha, til shunday usulda paydo bo'ladi:

00:08:28.260 --> 00:08:30.260
tovushlar

00:08:30.260 --> 00:08:33.260
tinglovchining subyektiv,

00:08:33.260 --> 00:08:35.260
shaxsiy,

00:08:35.260 --> 00:08:37.260
ichki sezish tajribalari bilan

00:08:37.260 --> 00:08:39.260
moslashadi, moyil keladi.

00:08:40.260 --> 00:08:43.260
Keling, uchinchi savolni ko'raylik.

00:08:44.260 --> 00:08:47.260
Bu John Keatsning she'ridan bir misra.

00:08:47.260 --> 00:08:50.260
So'zlar, huddi sonlar kabi,

00:08:50.260 --> 00:08:53.260
bizning olamimizni tashkil qiladigan

00:08:53.260 --> 00:08:55.260
narsalar, voqealar

00:08:55.260 --> 00:08:57.260
va kuchlar o'rtasidagi eng asosiy

00:08:57.260 --> 00:08:59.260
aloqalarni ifodalayadi.

00:08:59.260 --> 00:09:02.260
Biz, bu dunyoda yashab turib, hayotimiz davomida

00:09:02.260 --> 00:09:04.260
ana o'sha aloqalarni ichki hissiyot bilan

00:09:04.260 --> 00:09:07.260
sezishimiz kerakligi odatiy tuyuladi.

00:09:07.260 --> 00:09:10.260
Shoirlar, huddi boshqa rassomlar kabi,

00:09:10.260 --> 00:09:13.260
ana o'sha ichki sezgi tushunadigan narsalar bilan o'ynaydi.

00:09:13.260 --> 00:09:16.260
Inglizcha "hare" so'zi

00:09:16.260 --> 00:09:18.260
ingliz tilida noaniq tovushdir.

00:09:18.260 --> 00:09:21.260
Bu boshimizda o'sadigan soch tolalarni ham anglatishi mumkin.

00:09:21.260 --> 00:09:23.260
Agar biz bu haqida o'ylaak --

00:09:23.260 --> 00:09:25.260
rasmini sizlarga ko'rsatay --

00:09:25.260 --> 00:09:28.260
tolalar noziklikni tasvirlaydi.

00:09:29.260 --> 00:09:32.260
Ular yengilgina harakat,

00:09:32.260 --> 00:09:35.260
qimirlash yoki hissiyotga ta'sirchan, harakatga keluvchi bo'ladi.

00:09:35.260 --> 00:09:39.260
Hullas, noziklik (ta'sirchanlik) va

00:09:39.260 --> 00:09:41.260
taranglik holati paydo bo'ladi.

00:09:41.260 --> 00:09:43.260
"Hare" so'zi - quyon, hayvon --

00:09:43.260 --> 00:09:46.260
mushuk emas, it emas, "hare"-quyon --

00:09:46.260 --> 00:09:48.260
nimaga "hare"-quyon?

00:09:48.260 --> 00:09:50.260
Sababi, rasmni hayolingizga keltiring,

00:09:50.260 --> 00:09:52.260
so'zni emas, rasmni.

00:09:52.260 --> 00:09:54.260
Juda uzun quloqlar,

00:09:54.260 --> 00:09:56.260
juda katta oyoqlar

00:09:56.260 --> 00:09:59.260
"limp" - oqsoqlanish va "tremble" - qaltirash nimaligini

00:09:59.260 --> 00:10:02.260
ko'z oldimizda tasavvur qilishimizga, ichki hissiyot bilan sezishimizga

00:10:02.260 --> 00:10:05.260
yozrdam beradi.

00:10:05.260 --> 00:10:07.260
Mana shu oz daqiqalar davomida

00:10:07.260 --> 00:10:09.260
mening narsalar haqidagi nazarimni

00:10:09.260 --> 00:10:12.260
sizlarga tushuntirib bera oldim

00:10:12.260 --> 00:10:15.260
va so'zlar ham rang va hissiyotga,

00:10:15.260 --> 00:10:18.260
raqamlar, shakllar va shaxsiy xarakter, hususiyatlarga

00:10:18.260 --> 00:10:21.260
ega ekanligini sizlarga ko'rsata oldim deb umid qilaman.

00:10:21.260 --> 00:10:23.260
Dunyo bizga sezilganidan ko'ra

00:10:23.260 --> 00:10:25.260
boyroq

00:10:25.260 --> 00:10:28.260
va ulkanroqdir.

00:10:28.260 --> 00:10:31.260
Sizlarda dunyoni yangi ko'zlar bilan ko'rishni

00:10:31.260 --> 00:10:34.260
o'rganish xohishini uyg'otdim deb umid qilaman.

00:10:34.260 --> 00:10:36.260
Rahmat.

00:10:36.260 --> 00:10:47.260
(Qarsaklar)

